query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('academia',
'android',
'gamedev',
'gaming')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('3d',
'adb',
'career-path',
'conference',
'javascript',
'job-search',
'minecraft-pocket-edition',
'professors',
'ps3',
'shaders',
'terminology',
'united-states',
'writing')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 10
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
